dcterms:creator: M. D. Schirmer
Y. Leitner
dcterms:description: The CNI 2019 Challenge dataset consists of preprocessed resting state fMRI time series data provided for subjects diagnosed with Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD), Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD) with ADHD comorbidity, and healthy controls.
dcterms:title: CNI 2019 Challenge dataset

dcterms:creator: Y. Leitner
dcterms:description: The ADHD-ASD comorbidities dataset is part of the CNI 2019 Challenge dataset and focuses on the co-occurrence of autism and attention deficit hyperactivity disorder in children.
dcterms:title: ADHD-ASD comorbidities dataset
